            <title><![CDATA[中国前五个月住宅销售额同比下降34.5%]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>中国房地产市场进一步疲软，今年前五个月住宅销售额同比下降34.5%，</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>相比之下今年1月至4月同比下降32.2%，显示房地产市场前景并未好转。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>中国国家统计局今天（15日）公布的数据显示，今年1月至5月，中国商品房销售额为4万8337亿元（人民币，下同，约1万亿新元），下降31.5%；其中，住宅销售额下降34.5%。商品房销售面积同比下降23.6%；其中，住宅销售面积下降28.1%。5月末，商品房待售面积同比增长8.6%；其中，住宅待售面积增长15%。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>房地产开发投资方面，今年1月至5月，</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>全国房地产开发投资</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>5万2134</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>亿元，同比下降</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>4%</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>；其中，住宅投资</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>3万9521</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>3%</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
